<D>__{what do you think you're doing.}
<A>__{he walks over to the dock.}
<C>__{harbor master}
<D>__{all right friend, out of the boat.}
<A>__{he tries to board the boat but chuck greets him with the sharp end of a gaffing hook.}
<C>__{older chuck}
<P>__{(softly)}
<D>__{stand away.}
<A>__{he looks into chuck's eyes and sees that he means business. he backs off. chucks pushes away and raises the sail. the harbor master watches, perplexed as the small boat moves off for open water.}
